Old Master,

34
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,820
didn't you say that

35
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,229
once you get the formula for the sedative,

36
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,390
you'll be able to come back

37
00:03:05,730 --> 00:03:06,760
with Xia Guang Yuan in tow?

38
00:03:06,850 --> 00:03:08,150
There have been some changes.

39
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,000
The Chinese market had previously been

40
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:15,220
