44
00:03:24,330 --> 00:03:26,190
Particularly the youth in China.

45
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:29,020
Knowing what they like
and their preferences

46
00:03:29,170 --> 00:03:30,860
is key to securing future markets.

47
00:03:33,290 --> 00:03:35,070
This is T4's real opportunity.

48
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,600
Understood, Old Master.

49
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,900
