to treat your mother.

55
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,900
He's only using her to control you.

56
00:04:22,479 --> 00:04:24,540
Old Master isn't going to save my mother.

57
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:26,640
Is he?

58
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,820
When will we ever be able
to obtain all the data?

59
00:04:29,570 --> 00:04:31,620
The police would've probably
found us by then.

60
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:33,240
Not probably,

61
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,940
but definitely.

62
00:04:36,410 --> 00:04:37,280
Since the medical forum,

63
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,470
they've already been keeping an eye on us.

64
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,520
So what now?

65
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,880
What do you think?

66
00:04:44,970 --> 00:04:46,230
I think

67
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:48,020
we should just take the man away.

68
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,720
If we can't have Xia Guang Yuan,

69
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,210
at least we can get the daughter.

70
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,110
You're right.

71
00:05:08,850 --> 00:05:11,310
Doing things step by step like this
is too slow.

72
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:12,810
Some things

73
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:16,330
need to be wrapped up.

74
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:20,500
I'll leave Xia Chu to you.

75
00:05:21,090 --> 00:05:22,260
I'll sort out

76
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,660
the production.

77
00:05:23,980 --> 00:05:25,120
In two days,

78
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,870
we'll meet at the same place.

79
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:37,430
Commander Dong,

80
00:05:38,010 --> 00:05:39,970
Based on the comprehensive clues
we've gathered,

81
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,550
the prime suspect

82
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:44,030
should be Xia Chu's first boyfriend,

83
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,100
Zhuo Ran.

84
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:46,720
That man

85
00:05:46,809 --> 00:05:48,790
has had numerous altercations with Mu Ze.

86
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:51,059
It looks like

87
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:53,020
he still hasn't gotten over Xia Chu.

88
00:05:53,559 --> 00:05:56,320
So you think he has a clear motive?

89
00:05:56,410 --> 00:05:57,300
That's right.

90
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:58,830
I've sent men

91
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,090
to conduct surveillance on him.

92
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,150
If this case

93
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:02,670
is indeed related to him,

94
00:06:03,010 --> 00:06:04,500
he should've known

95
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,020
that the tapping device was discovered.

96
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:08,100
We're expecting him to take action.

97
00:06:22,370 --> 00:06:24,390
Long Yi

98
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,500
I've arrived at her neighbourhood.

99
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,220
We'll act in one hour.

100
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,780
What's happening, Lei?

101
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,070
You may go in, mister.

102
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,160
Call the captain.

103
00:06:58,250 --> 00:06:59,120
Okay.

104
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:00,460
I got the picture now.

105
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,250
What do you want our unit to do?

106
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,980
The two people living at Mu Ze's house

107
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:07,060
are the witness of the case, Xia Chu,

108
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,440
and

109
00:07:09,250 --> 00:07:10,910
Mu Ze's cousin, Liang Shao Xue.

110
00:07:12,670 --> 00:07:14,880
I propose that before things
are sorted out,

111
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,790
they be moved

112
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,100
to somewhere more secure.

113
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:19,130
No problem.

114
00:07:19,250 --> 00:07:20,160
The Special Forces Brigade

115
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:22,140
can provide shelter and security.

116
00:07:25,030 --> 00:07:25,910
Mu Ze.

117
00:07:27,290 --> 00:07:28,510
Any other concerns?

118
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:36,060
-Let me take this call.
-Okay.

119
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,740
Where?

120
00:07:45,650 --> 00:07:46,530
Okay.

121
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,140
Got it. I'll be right there.

122
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,059
Zhuo Ran turned himself in.

123
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,580
Yes.

124
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:01,260
I installed the tapping device.

125
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,830
Why did you do it?

126
00:08:04,690 --> 00:08:06,180
Because I wish to get Xia Chu back.

127
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,040
I wanted to know

128
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:09,670
what she's doing at home

129
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:11,270
every moment of the day.

130
00:08:12,130 --> 00:08:13,870
I want to know everything about her.

131
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:16,070
To make up for the eight years

132
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,380
that I wasn't with her.

133
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:21,170
Do you know who that house belongs to?

134
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:23,630
I didn't know at first.

135
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,070
The day I installed the device,

136
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:29,140
I almost ran into him.

137
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:35,830
Meaning to say,

138
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,829
through the tapping device,

139
00:08:38,170 --> 00:08:40,980
you learned that Xia Chu wanted
to give Liang Mu Ze tranquillisers.

140
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,350
So you purposely switched it.

141
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,020
Right?

142
00:08:45,329 --> 00:08:47,510
Yes, it was overheard on the device.

143
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,740
But I wasn't the one who heard it.

144
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,940
It was Long Yi.

145
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,180
He's my assistant.

146
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,240
He was the one who switched the pills.

147
00:09:07,450 --> 00:09:08,750
Why would he do that?

148
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:10,520
Because Old Master told him to.

149
00:09:10,650 --> 00:09:11,750
"Old Master"?

150
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,530
He's the founder of T4.

151
00:09:15,350 --> 00:09:16,910
The terrorist attack

152
00:09:17,010 --> 00:09:19,430
that happened at the medical
headquarters in Isaia,

153
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,070
that was T4's doing?

154
00:09:22,660 --> 00:09:23,780
Back then,

155
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:26,280
he smuggled into Willick from China.

156
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,340
Under the code name T4,

157
00:09:28,430 --> 00:09:30,090
he set up his own army of mercenaries.

158
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:33,080
On the surface, he operated
under the pretence of trade investment,

159
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,660
but in actual fact,

160
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:36,760
the things he did were illegal.

161
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,730
What is his real name?

162
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,930
I don't know.

163
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:41,850
From the first time I met him,

164
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,180
I've been calling him Old Master.

165
00:09:43,450 --> 00:09:45,040
As for his history in China,

166
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:46,910
I do not know either.

167
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,410
How did you two meet?

168
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,720
In my final year of high school,

169
00:09:51,110 --> 00:09:52,650
a distant relative

170
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:55,020
had arranged for my mother
to be treated in Willick.

171
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:58,870
We ended up at an illegal factory.

172
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,940
There,

173
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,640
we endured a very dark time.

174
00:10:03,890 --> 00:10:05,790
We finally managed to escape.

175
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:08,270
But we ended up almost starving
to death on the streets.

176
00:10:09,060 --> 00:10:10,520
It was Old Master that saved us.

177
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:13,320
He gave us a place to feel safe.

178
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,120
He even paid for my education.

179
00:10:17,070 --> 00:10:18,610
So in the beginning,

180
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:20,420
I was very grateful towards him.

181
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:22,380
You could say

182
00:10:22,780 --> 00:10:23,950
I relied on him.

183
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:27,630
Until...

184
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:28,980
Until what?

185
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:31,150
Until I graduated university,

186
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:33,030
he started to let me

187
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,230
take over some accounts of the company.

188
00:10:35,450 --> 00:10:36,900
That's when I realised

189
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:39,570
the ugly truth behind
his so-called company.

190
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,980
I didn't want to help him.

191
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:44,040
I tried to make him stop.

192
00:10:44,610 --> 00:10:46,350
But why would he listen to me?

193
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,620
If you are against his ways,

194
00:10:54,690 --> 00:10:56,260
why do you still work for him?

195
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:58,900
He has my mother.

196
00:10:59,530 --> 00:11:00,780
I have no choice.

197
00:11:01,420 --> 00:11:03,080
He's been trying to groom me

198
00:11:03,170 --> 00:11:04,460
as his right-hand man.

199
00:11:04,810 --> 00:11:06,680
I've done all I could

200
00:11:07,010 --> 00:11:09,430
to not get involved in matters
outside of the finances.

201
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:12,410
But knowing that
my mother's safety is at risk,

202
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:15,540
I'm not sure how much more I can take.

203
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,470
So you came to Ningjiang

204
00:11:20,770 --> 00:11:22,620
because Old Master told you to?

205
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,000
Yes.

206
00:11:26,290 --> 00:11:28,710
He wants me to find Sang Kun's
younger brother, Gui.

207
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,700
Then he sent his underling, Long Yi,

208
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,750
to become my assistant

209
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,880
in order to monitor me.

210
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:40,480
So have you found Gui?

211
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:41,950
We have.

212
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:44,130
But I only found out later

213
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:45,640
that Long Yi had killed Gui

214
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,380
behind my back.

215
00:11:48,290 --> 00:11:49,780
And on the day itself,

216
00:11:50,350 --> 00:11:52,060
he almost went head to head
with you people.

217
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,940
He downloaded a program online

218
00:11:55,450 --> 00:11:57,220
and printed a 3D gun.

219
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,150
And then,

220
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,860
he sneaked Gui out of the hospital,

221
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:02,050
shot him

222
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,280
and set up the crime scene.

223
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:09,260
What about you?

224
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,220
What was your role

225
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:14,550
in all of this?

226
00:12:15,050 --> 00:12:16,510
I'm a victim.

227
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,550
I'm bearing the risks of being found out

228
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,730
and losing my mother

229
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,340
by coming here to tell you guys this.

230
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:27,030
You have to ensure my safety.

231
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:31,500
I no longer want to live like a dog.

232
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:34,070
This isn't the kind of life I want.

233
00:12:35,050 --> 00:12:36,540
I've had enough.

234
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,440
Even in my dreams, I tried
to escape from the shackles he put on me,

235
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,700
but I couldn't.

236
00:12:41,340 --> 00:12:42,560
Everything I do

237
00:12:42,650 --> 00:12:44,860
gets reported to Old Master.

238
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,540
My mother's life may be in danger.

239
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:48,910
And Xia Chu.

240
00:12:49,690 --> 00:12:50,790
What about Xia Chu?

241
00:12:52,770 --> 00:12:54,150
He knows

242
00:12:54,850 --> 00:12:56,990
how much Xia Chu means to me.

243
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,640
Just like how he's using
my mother to control me,

244
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,500
he wants to do the same with Xia Chu.

245
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,150
Use her to force me

246
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,060
to establish drug trafficking
channels in China,

247
00:13:05,210 --> 00:13:06,710
to be his accomplice in crime.

248
00:13:07,410 --> 00:13:08,990
I can only try my best

249
00:13:09,090 --> 00:13:10,430
to buy time.

250
00:13:11,040 --> 00:13:12,900
But with me...

251
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:15,200
By myself,

252
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:17,230
there's no way for me to stop him.

253
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:19,110
For the sake of the two most
important women in my life,

254
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,620
I'm begging you.

255
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,940
I'm willing to cooperate with the police

256
00:13:23,370 --> 00:13:25,110
to bring Old Master to justice.

257
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,900
Officer Rao.

258
00:13:28,680 --> 00:13:30,780
I know you must be dubious

259
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,900
about what I just said.

260
00:13:33,780 --> 00:13:34,810
It's fine.

261
00:13:34,970 --> 00:13:36,560
You can verify it later.

262
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:37,900
But right now,

263
00:13:37,990 --> 00:13:40,330
you need to send men
to Liang Mu Ze's house.

264
00:13:40,890 --> 00:13:42,390
Because Old Master has given the order

265
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:44,430
for Long Yi to take care of Xia Chu.

266
00:14:19,370 --> 00:14:20,420
Is there no electricity?

267
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:22,880
I don't know. I was watching a drama

268
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:24,190
and the Internet suddenly stopped.

269
00:14:30,850 --> 00:14:31,730
Hello.

270
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:32,960
Hi, Ms Xia.

271
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:34,680
Please come to the building
management office.

272
00:14:35,390 --> 00:14:36,420
What's the matter?

273
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:38,450
There's a problem
with your house's electricity meter.

274
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:39,450
We need to check with you

275
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:40,840
before we can fix the problem.

276
00:14:41,090 --> 00:14:42,270
What's the problem?

277
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:47,660
What's up?

278
00:14:49,020 --> 00:14:50,840
Something is wrong with
the electricity meter.

279
00:14:51,130 --> 00:14:53,160
No wonder the hair dryer
suddenly stopped working.

280
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,920
I'm going to the management office.

281
00:14:55,010 --> 00:14:56,350
Stay here and be good.

282
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,120
Alright.

283
00:15:16,690 --> 00:15:18,110
"Ms Xia"?

284
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,130
Liang Mu Ze!

285
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:57,220
No matter how fast the lift is,

286
00:15:57,410 --> 00:15:58,400
within three storeys,

287
00:15:58,490 --> 00:16:00,310
a human running can easily
catch up to it.

288
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:02,240
So if there's an emergency

289
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,750
and you have to take the lift,

290
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:05,360
make sure it goes
more than three storeys.

291
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:06,590
If needed,

292
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:08,680
press a few more floors
to confuse the pursuer.

293
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,430
Anything you find around you

294
00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:19,490
can be used as a makeshift weapon.

295
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:26,240
If you can't get away,

296
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:29,140
try your best to go somewhere
with people

297
00:16:29,310 --> 00:16:30,600
and call for help.

298
00:16:37,890 --> 00:16:39,880
Fire! Fire!

299
00:16:40,090 --> 00:16:41,030
Evacuate!

300
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,820
-Fire!
-Forget about the things!

301
00:17:27,530 --> 00:17:28,540
Are you okay?

302
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,550
Someone's after me.

303
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:30,650
I didn't see his face.

304
00:17:30,759 --> 00:17:32,239
He addressed me as Ms Xia on the phone.

305
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:33,840
But I never registered with
the building management.

306
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,630
So I'm pretty sure he came for me.

307
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,300
I was reaching the basement.

308
00:17:37,410 --> 00:17:38,870
I turned and ran just like you taught me.

309
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,140
I pressed several floors in the lift.

310
00:17:40,300 --> 00:17:41,640
I got off halfway

311
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,710
because I thought someone
might be waiting there.

312
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:48,390
You did good.

313
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,240
It's okay now.

314
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:51,830
I'm here.

315
00:17:57,910 --> 00:17:58,700
When the incident occurred,

316
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,460
it happened to be the change of shifts.

317
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:02,650
There was no one
in the night shift office.

318
00:18:03,010 --> 00:18:03,890
Rao Zhi.

319
00:18:04,370 --> 00:18:05,250
Anything?

320
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:06,740
Li Lei and the rest are
at the basement car park.

321
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:08,180
The management staff and I

322
00:18:08,270 --> 00:18:09,820
have checked the floors of the building.

323
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,200
We didn't find anyone suspicious.

324
00:18:11,280 --> 00:18:13,110
The culprit probably sneaked out

325
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,810
in the minutes following the alarm.

326
00:18:16,710 --> 00:18:18,090
We'd like to check the CCTVs.

327
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:19,400
Sure, come with me.

328
00:18:21,490 --> 00:18:23,630
Alright, guys. Follow me.

329
00:18:25,900 --> 00:18:27,200
Okay, pay attention.

330
00:18:27,290 --> 00:18:28,140
Thank you, everyone.

331
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:29,640
Please wait here for a bit.

332
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,290
Go with him.

333
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:32,260
Okay.

334
00:18:35,650 --> 00:18:36,400
We're sorting it out.

335
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,230
Please remain calm.

336
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:38,200
Xue.

337
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,180
Do you have time?

338
00:18:43,780 --> 00:18:44,950
I'd like to talk to you.

339
00:18:45,770 --> 00:18:48,230
Thank you for your cooperation.
Please wait here.

340
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,070
Yes, I'm at home.

341
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:54,040
Okay, got it.

342
00:18:54,130 --> 00:18:55,180
Okay.

343
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,740
Xue is with her dad.

344
00:19:02,810 --> 00:19:03,790
That's good.

345
00:19:04,210 --> 00:19:05,600
Did the police catch the culprit?

346
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:07,330
Who is he?

347
00:19:07,730 --> 00:19:08,680
Why did he come after me?

348
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:09,780
Don't ask.

349
00:19:11,610 --> 00:19:12,660
Is that confidential?

350
00:19:12,930 --> 00:19:13,810
Yes.

351
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:17,260
Alright.

352
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:21,480
Xia Chu.

353
00:19:24,550 --> 00:19:26,500
I have to return to the unit
before lights-out.

354
00:19:30,050 --> 00:19:31,360
Your break is over?

355
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,150
Come along with me.

356
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:40,380
I don't mean anything else.

357
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:42,420
It's much safer at the unit.

358
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:44,080
It will be the same as last time.

359
00:19:44,170 --> 00:19:45,390
You'll stay at the guest lodging.

360
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,500
I'll be at the barracks.

361
00:19:47,990 --> 00:19:50,470
Commander Dong has spoken to the chief.

362
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:51,390
You're welcome any time.

363
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,380
Thank you, guys.

364
00:19:56,410 --> 00:19:57,340
I understand.

365
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,790
You're doing this for my own good.

366
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,990
Including your timely appearance today.

367
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,550
I'm very grateful.

368
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:07,690
Get to the point.

369
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:09,590
But I can't go.

370
00:20:10,010 --> 00:20:11,200
At least not now.

371
00:20:12,810 --> 00:20:14,730
The ER is short-handed.

372
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,280
If I leave without notice,

373
00:20:16,720 --> 00:20:17,910
it will only cause more stress

374
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,420
to my colleagues.

375
00:20:20,490 --> 00:20:21,450
Besides,

376
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:24,340
the patients I'm currently
looking after in ER

377
00:20:24,490 --> 00:20:25,790
haven't been released to normal care.

378
00:20:26,050 --> 00:20:28,150
I have to follow up
when I get back to work.

379
00:20:30,170 --> 00:20:31,670
As for my personal safety,

380
00:20:31,770 --> 00:20:32,790
don't you worry.

381
00:20:33,180 --> 00:20:34,810
I'll protect myself well.

382
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:36,610
I'll carry pepper spray with me.

383
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,540
I won't take dark alleys,

384
00:20:37,620 --> 00:20:38,600
won't go to secluded places,

385
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:39,750
won't simply open the door.

386
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:40,790
I won't give any chances

387
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,420
to the bad guys to get close.

388
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:46,700
Is that

389
00:20:48,050 --> 00:20:49,170
okay with you?

390
00:20:58,010 --> 00:20:58,890
Alright.

391
00:21:02,650 --> 00:21:03,820
I have to go to the hospital.

392
00:21:05,930 --> 00:21:06,810
I'll take you.

393
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:09,130
Okay.

394
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:14,030
Sun Xiao Mo,

395
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:15,520
you and Li Lei will split up.

396
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:17,260
You'll continue to locate Long Yi.

397
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:19,210
Ask Li Lei to send two men
to the hospital.

398
00:21:19,610 --> 00:21:20,800
Before we find Long Yi,

399
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,330
he's in charge of Dr Xia's safety.

400
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:23,030
Alright?

401
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:24,440
Notify me if anything.

402
00:21:34,080 --> 00:21:35,550
Get down here.

403
00:21:36,020 --> 00:21:37,530
Leaning out like that is dangerous!

404
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:38,690
What if you fell?

405
00:21:38,830 --> 00:21:40,280
I'm already 21.

406
00:21:40,370 --> 00:21:41,920
I've come across countless
dangerous situations.

407
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,820
Since when have you come to my rescue?

408
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:48,330
Speak. What's the matter?

409
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:49,860
What do you mean?

410
00:21:52,290 --> 00:21:53,520
Didn't you tell Mu Ze

411
00:21:53,610 --> 00:21:55,150
that you'd only speak in front of me?

412
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,340
You escorted me to the police station
so early in the day

413
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:01,140
and disappeared with my bag.

414
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,960
I waited an hour here for you

415
00:22:03,050 --> 00:22:04,260
and this is what it's about?

416
00:22:04,340 --> 00:22:06,140
You could very well be a witness.

417
00:22:06,230 --> 00:22:07,400
I have someone I like.

418
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:09,050
I'm not asking about that.

419
00:22:09,140 --> 00:22:10,330
But I want to talk about it.

420
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,650
Two nights ago,

421
00:22:11,740 --> 00:22:13,200
you went to Yunshan Tunnel, right?

422
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:14,530
Why should I tell you?

423
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,510
What time did you go?

424
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:16,510
Did you see anyone there?

425
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:17,480
Take a guess.

426
00:22:18,160 --> 00:22:18,710
Guess.

427
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:19,990
Xue.

428
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:22,250
This is very important.

429
00:22:22,340 --> 00:22:23,500
I don't care a lick.

430
00:22:23,580 --> 00:22:24,530
Mind your tone.

431
00:22:25,010 --> 00:22:26,450
I'm not one of your suspects.

432
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:28,010
I don't have to be interrogated.

433
00:22:28,090 --> 00:22:29,800
You want to talk to me? Sure.

434
00:22:30,080 --> 00:22:31,640
Resign from this stupid job

435
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,970
and come to the US with me.

436
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:34,530
We'll have a meal with Mum.

437
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:35,530
While eating,

438
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:37,130
I'll be glad to chat with you.

439
00:22:37,280 --> 00:22:38,530
But here,

440
00:22:38,620 --> 00:22:40,420
I'm not saying one word.

441
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:44,650
Xue.

442
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,450
Xue!

443
00:22:50,260 --> 00:22:52,130
Who is the guy you like?

444
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:05,910
Liu Ran.

445
00:23:06,450 --> 00:23:07,470
How do you feel?

446
00:23:10,050 --> 00:23:11,150
Miss Xia Chu.

447
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:14,350
The doctor said my numbers

448
00:23:14,430 --> 00:23:15,780
have returned to normal.

449
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:19,100
Am I going to be discharged soon?

450
00:23:19,650 --> 00:23:21,740
That will depend on your overall recovery.

451
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,710
Dr Zhang will decide when you do.

452
00:23:40,060 --> 00:23:41,160
What's on your mind?

453
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:50,400
If...

454
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,080
If my dad could see how

455
00:23:53,160 --> 00:23:54,860
I overcame this,

456
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,830
he would be proud, wouldn't he?

457
00:24:04,690 --> 00:24:05,840
From now on,

458
00:24:06,290 --> 00:24:07,270
I will

459
00:24:07,770 --> 00:24:09,110
do as you said.

460
00:24:11,140 --> 00:24:12,630
I will live

461
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,510
for his sake as well.

462
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,220
You can cry.

463
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:32,100
Cry all you want.

464
00:24:33,320 --> 00:24:34,740
You'll feel better after.

465
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,860
Dr Xia.

466
00:24:51,480 --> 00:24:52,710
I want to make a police report.

467
00:25:03,360 --> 00:25:04,240
Are you

468
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:06,210
sure?

469
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:14,760
This is the hospital's

470
00:25:14,850 --> 00:25:16,350
first successful case of saving

471
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,550
a patient poisoned by paraquat

472
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,470
with supplementary therapy using ECMO.

473
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:22,020
How long was ECMO

474
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:23,740
installed on the patient?

475
00:25:24,190 --> 00:25:25,910
Including the waiting time
for the organ,

476
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:26,720
seven days.

477
00:25:26,800 --> 00:25:27,960
I see. Seven days.

478
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:28,930
Okay.

479
00:25:29,250 --> 00:25:31,160
Try to utilise ECMO outside
of the operating room

480
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:32,150
and into

481
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:34,110
the emergency care of severe cases.

482
00:25:34,560 --> 00:25:35,350
It will be beneficial

483
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:37,350
to the establishment of the hospital's

484
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,100
emergency response system.

485
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:45,060
Xia Chu.

486
00:25:55,210 --> 00:25:56,090
Mr Zhang.

487
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:57,720
Sir.

488
00:25:57,810 --> 00:25:59,230
Let me introduce to you

489
00:25:59,330 --> 00:26:00,280
Xia Chu.

490
00:26:00,410 --> 00:26:01,830
A top student
from the Military Medical University.

491
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:04,450
She obtained her Physician's License
two years after graduating.

492
00:26:04,620 --> 00:26:06,330
She's completed the regulatory training

493
00:26:06,410 --> 00:26:08,760
and was previously stationed at
Cardiac Surgery Department.

494
00:26:09,430 --> 00:26:10,660
Her performance has been outstanding.

495
00:26:10,770 --> 00:26:11,830
Right, Dr Chen?

496
00:26:12,730 --> 00:26:14,070
Now at ER,

497
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:16,670
she played a part in rescuing Liu Ran.

498
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:18,530
I know her.

499
00:26:20,860 --> 00:26:22,010
For the past two months,

500
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:23,910
I've been conducting
experiential research

501
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:26,470
on the various departments
at the hospital.

502
00:26:26,570 --> 00:26:28,140
I bumped into one time.

503
00:26:29,930 --> 00:26:30,880
That day,

504
00:26:31,010 --> 00:26:32,510
she was totally drenched.

505
00:26:33,090 --> 00:26:34,200
She was pulling a cooler box

506
00:26:34,290 --> 00:26:36,280
containing an organ for transplant,

507
00:26:36,370 --> 00:26:37,790
running towards the operating room.

508
00:26:42,040 --> 00:26:43,020
Do you remember?

509
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,520
So that was you.

510
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:48,660
That's right.

511
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:52,350
This young lady looks gentle and meek,

512
00:26:52,450 --> 00:26:53,510
but when carrying out her duty,

513
00:26:53,600 --> 00:26:54,830
she's full of vigour.

514
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,520
You know how things are at this hospital.

515
00:26:56,610 --> 00:26:57,430
Over here,

516
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,720
women are treated like men,

517
00:26:58,810 --> 00:27:00,270
men are treated like livestock.

518
00:27:00,570 --> 00:27:01,540
You joke.

519
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:03,930
She's always the one going the distance.

520
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:06,570
Sir, you're exaggerating.

521
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:08,880
I am just carrying out my duty, is all.

522
00:27:10,820 --> 00:27:11,840
Yes, good.

523
00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:13,470
Let's go and check on the patients.

524
00:27:13,720 --> 00:27:14,920
Okay. See you.

525
00:27:15,010 --> 00:27:15,890
See you.

526
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,860
During lunch break,

527
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,580
come to see me in my office.

528
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:39,450
You're still here.

529
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,120
Yeah.

530
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:45,210
If the 4S shop calls,

531
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,600
go and get the car.

532
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:49,910
You're asking me to drive?

533
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:51,730
You need practice.

534
00:27:52,030 --> 00:27:53,740
It's a necessary life skill.

535
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:55,370
Next time, you can run faster.

536
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:57,480
Okay.

537
00:27:57,810 --> 00:27:58,690
I'm off then.

538
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:01,780
Liang Mu Ze.

539
00:28:06,630 --> 00:28:08,020
From a professional standpoint,

540
00:28:09,170 --> 00:28:10,500
I am considered half your comrade.

541
00:28:13,190 --> 00:28:14,600
I know the meaning

542
00:28:14,770 --> 00:28:16,310
of the military uniform to you.

543
00:28:17,370 --> 00:28:18,540
In one's life,

544
00:28:18,820 --> 00:28:19,970
how much they earn,

545
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:21,480
what kind of house they own,

546
00:28:21,770 --> 00:28:22,990
what car they drive,

547
00:28:23,500 --> 00:28:24,970
those are all done for others.

548
00:28:25,910 --> 00:28:27,220
There's only one thing,

549
00:28:27,890 --> 00:28:29,570
what kind of person you wish to become,

550
00:28:29,860 --> 00:28:31,160
is done for yourself.

551
00:28:33,380 --> 00:28:34,930
Staying true to oneself is hard.

552
00:28:35,510 --> 00:28:37,930
Perhaps it's a life-long lesson
we continue to master.

553
00:28:38,570 --> 00:28:39,910
I am still a newbie.

554
00:28:40,790 --> 00:28:41,940
So I'm sorry.

555
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:44,290
I can't give you better advice.

556
00:28:45,330 --> 00:28:46,640
But I'd like you to know

557
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:49,560
that your decisions
are always right, Captain Liang.

558
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:51,740
I believe...

559
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:00,460
Liang Mu Ze, this is the hospital.

560
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,380
You asked me before

561
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,650
if anyone's habit

562
00:29:10,860 --> 00:29:12,200
is found in my life.

563
00:29:12,510 --> 00:29:13,490
You said no.

564
00:29:13,570 --> 00:29:14,630
Not at that time.

565
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,540
But now, I'm telling you

566
00:29:16,910 --> 00:29:18,280
I'm learning to eat durian.

567
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:21,170
I'm learning to omit the salt
when cooking soup.

568
00:29:22,650 --> 00:29:24,070
I've gotten used to your taste buds.

569
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:26,260
I remember what you said about

570
00:29:26,390 --> 00:29:28,160
the heart being on top of the stomach.

571
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:31,990
I no longer want to be
even with you, Dr Xia.

