00:43:10,250 --> 00:43:11,140
And the rest?

849
00:43:11,400 --> 00:43:12,280
The rest?

850
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:14,650
Rest of what?

851
00:43:14,740 --> 00:43:16,210
Why did Long Yi target Xia Chu?

852
00:43:16,300 --> 00:43:17,450
That's Old Master's order.

853
00:43:17,530 --> 00:43:18,730
Why did Old Master give that order?

854
00:43:18,890 --> 00:43:19,680
I don't know.

855
00:43:19,770 --> 00:43:21,460
What exactly is your relationship
with Old Master?

856
00:43:22,150 --> 00:43:23,620
I've told you everything.

857
00:43:23,910 --> 00:43:25,900
In spite of the threats
from the evildoers,

858
00:43:26,370 --> 00:43:27,630
I've come clean about my mistake.

859
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:28,740
I turned myself in

860
00:43:28,830 --> 00:43:30,250
and am cooperating with you.

861
00:43:30,340 --> 00:43:31,710
I'm not hoping for any recognition.

862
00:43:32,090 --> 00:43:34,510
I just want to be reunited with my mother.

863
00:43:35,400 --> 00:43:36,420
If you don't believe me,

864
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:38,180
go ahead and verify it.

865
00:43:38,580 --> 00:43:39,960
But you better do it quickly.

866
00:43:40,240 --> 00:43:41,490
Time is ticking.

867
00:43:45,980 --> 00:43:47,580
Of course we'll verify it
as soon as possible.

868
00:43:48,550 --> 00:43:49,730
Since you

869
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:51,710
are so willing to cooperate with us

870
00:43:51,890 --> 00:43:53,470
and have provided us with important clues,

871
00:43:53,790 --> 00:43:55,600
we will ensure your personal safety.

872
00:43:56,090 --> 00:43:57,190
So,

873
00:43:57,480 --> 00:43:58,760
I hope you don't mind

874
00:43:58,850 --> 00:44:00,150
spending the night
at the detention centre.

875
00:44:04,390 --> 00:44:05,960
Certainly, Officer Rao.

876
00:44:22,490 --> 00:44:23,500
What are you doing here?

877
00:44:24,320 --> 00:44:25,940
I came to visit the parrot.

878
00:44:26,660 --> 00:44:27,520
Get in.

879
00:44:27,650 --> 00:44:28,640
You get off.

880
00:44:38,330 --> 00:44:39,390
Roger that.

881
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:43,020
Everyone, ready to deploy parachutes.

882
00:44:43,480 --> 00:44:45,510
Stand up. Clip on the snap hook.

883
00:45:04,930 --> 00:45:05,920
I don't understand.

884
00:45:06,730 --> 00:45:09,220
Why is his job more important
to him than family?

885
00:45:09,550 --> 00:45:12,010
Catching criminals is more important
than his daughter's happiness.

886
00:45:12,660 --> 00:45:14,450
He's trying to destroy my confidence

887
00:45:14,550 --> 00:45:17,250
towards men, love and marriage.

888
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:20,670
He hasn't had a wink of sleep
in three days, Xue.

889
00:45:20,760 --> 00:45:21,940
Why is that my problem?

890
00:45:22,050 --> 00:45:23,150
I don't care.

891
00:45:23,450 --> 00:45:24,670
He asked for it himself.

892
00:45:25,120 --> 00:45:27,510
He's forgotten that he's a husband
first and foremost,

893
00:45:27,590 --> 00:45:28,920
and a father next,

894
00:45:29,010 --> 00:45:30,550
and a police officer last.

895
00:45:31,030 --> 00:45:32,100
Tell me then.

896
00:45:32,190 --> 00:45:33,120
What about the way

897
00:45:33,200 --> 00:45:35,680
you express your feelings
so heatedly and aggressively?

898
00:45:35,770 --> 00:45:36,750
I did not.

899
00:45:40,090 --> 00:45:40,990
Xue.

900
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,620
He is your birth father.

901
00:45:43,960 --> 00:45:44,840
Right?

902
00:45:45,200 --> 00:45:46,480
Just because he doesn't show

903
00:45:46,570 --> 00:45:47,800
his emotions as openly as you,

904
00:45:47,890 --> 00:45:49,550
doesn't mean you're not important.

905
00:45:49,640 --> 00:45:51,020
I'm not important.

906
00:45:52,090 --> 00:45:53,830
He's just cold-blooded.

907
00:46:03,980 --> 00:46:04,930
Are you alright?

908
00:46:09,080 --> 00:46:10,150
Tian Yong!

909
00:46:10,930 --> 00:46:11,710
Are you okay?

910
00:46:11,800 --> 00:46:12,560
Yeah.

911
00:46:12,650 --> 00:46:13,320
You should be ashamed.

912
00:46:13,410 --> 00:46:15,300
You're an experienced paratrooper
but still got caught in a tree?

913
00:46:15,390 --> 00:46:16,490
It's not his fault.

914
00:46:17,750 --> 00:46:19,910
He was trying to help the new recruit
open the parachute.

915
00:46:20,130 --> 00:46:21,670
That's why he drifted off course.

916
00:46:22,020 --> 00:46:22,920
Are you okay?

917
00:46:23,160 --> 00:46:24,150
Reporting, sir!

918
00:46:24,260 --> 00:46:25,130
I can still jump!

919
00:46:25,220 --> 00:46:26,130
Still jump?

920
00:46:26,240 --> 00:46:27,420
Look at the state you're in!

921
00:46:27,960 --> 00:46:28,910
I'm fine.

922
00:46:32,270 --> 00:46:33,670
Help him. Quick!

923
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:35,220
Get him to the infirmary.

